  <summary date="2020-05-21T12:24:40Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Coronavirus Relief Fund Flexibility Act

This bill allows Coronavirus Relief Fund payments to be used to replace state, tribal, or local government revenue shortfalls resulting from COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) during the period from March 1-December 31, 2020.</summary>
